      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model selection justified with literature support. Contact formulation validated against known analytical solutions for Hertzian contact.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity (BISO) selected for titanium alloy screw based on published tensile coupon data (ASTM E8). Augmented Lagrange contact with friction coefficient 0.2 validated against Hertzian analytical solution (error < 2%). Model form uncertainty quantified via sensitivity analysis across ±10% material parameter range."
