      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and yield strength derived from 12 Ti-6Al-4V tensile coupons from the same material lot as test specimens (E = 113.8 ± 2.1 GPa, σ_y = 896 ± 14 MPa). Screw geometry from CMM measurements (±5 µm). LHS uncertainty propagation (N=200 samples) produced 95th-percentile input uncertainty band of ±3.1% on stiffness QoI."
