      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested: n=6 at Laboratory A (FDA CDRH biomechanics lab) and n=5 at Laboratory B (DePuy Synthes test facility). All specimens traced to manufacturing lot NC-7.5-2022-04. Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation for stiffness = 4.2%, confirming reproducibility."
