      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA inputs (geometry, material, BCs) demonstrably equivalent to physical test specimen parameters within measurement uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "FEA geometry reconstructed from CMM scans of each individual test specimen. Material inputs from lot-matched coupon data. Boundary conditions replicate F1717 fixture kinematics (pin-pin, 5° offset). Equivalency formally demonstrated via input parameter mapping table reviewed by test laboratory personnel."
