      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 8.4 for all three QoIs: stiffness 1.41, yield force 1.63, force at 40 mm 1.78 — all below 1.96 threshold. Percentage differences 6.8%, 4.2%, 7.9% — all below 10% acceptance bound. Combined simulation (uSN) and experimental (uD) uncertainties propagated per RSS. All three QoIs pass both acceptance criteria."
    },
